F(n,m,k)= \sum_{j=0}^{\lfloor n/m \rfloor} (-1)^j {k \choose j}{n+k - j \, m -1 \choose k-1}
C(n,m,k) = k \, F(n-m,m,k-1) + F(n,m,k) 
C(3,2,3) = 3 \, F(1,2,2) + F(3,2,3) = 3 \times 2 + 1 = 7
